{"id":92654,"title":"Case report: Non-invasive management of Madura foot with oral posaconazole and ciprofloxacin.","abstract":"Madura foot is a chronic infection caused by fungus and/or bacteria. Traditionally, treatment has been surgical debridement or amputation. Non-invasive management with long-term antimicrobials alone has been reported as successful. We report a case of Madura foot in a Somali refugee successfully managed with oral posaconazole and ciprofloxacin. ","date":"2014-12-04","categories":"Skin and Connective Tissue Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25349373","annotations":[{"name":"Bacteria","weight":0.819111,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bacteria"},{"name":"Debridement","weight":0.798987,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Debridement"},{"name":"Chronic (medicine)","weight":0.783378,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chronic_(medicine)"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.728515,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.691549,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Fungus","weight":0.668921,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fungus"},{"name":"Amputation","weight":0.561425,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amputation"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.506431,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Ciprofloxacin","weight":0.44911,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ciprofloxacin"},{"name":"Posaconazole","weight":0.44911,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Posaconazole"},{"name":"Mouth","weight":0.435087,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouth"},{"name":"Antimicrobial","weight":0.233385,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antimicrobial"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.20545,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"},{"name":"Foot","weight":0.137544,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foot"},{"name":"Refugee","weight":0.0960514,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Refugee"},{"name":"Invasiveness of surgical procedures","weight":0.0422207,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Invasiveness_of_surgical_procedures"},{"name":"Somalia","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Somalia"},{"name":"Madura Island","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madura_Island"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0185779,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Case Western Reserve University","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_Western_Reserve_University"}]}
